<1ST_LINE>r i AM-Britain-SouthAfrica     06-13 0330</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Britain-South Africa,0344</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Exiled Lawyer Says South African Government Attempted His Murder</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A South African lawyer whose arm was blown off in
an April car-bomb explosion alleged Monday that the South African
government planted the bomb as part of a death campaign against
African National Congress members.
   South African officials denied it.
   Albie Sachs, 53, is a white member of the ANC, the main
guerrilla group fighting the South African government.
   The exiled attorney said the government was responsible for the
April 7 attack in the Mozambique capital of Maputo.
   ``It was an arm, almost certainly the military arm, of
Pretoria,'' said Sachs, who spoke in a television interview from an
undisclosed location in Britain.
   ``They've been doing it in many parts of the world. They've
threatened to kill ANC people wherever they might be anywhere in
the world,'' said Sachs, who looked ill as he spoke, with the stump
of his arm still bandaged. Sachs was also burned and his eye
injured in the explosion.
   ``They are the only people who have the possible motivation and
capacity for this kind of thing,'' he said.
   Independent Television, which carried the interview, said Sachs
was secretly flown to London for medical treatment after the
explosion, which blew apart his car. At the time of the blast,
Sachs was employed by the Mozambican Justice Ministry.
   The television station said Sachs has been living in Britain
under an assumed name.
   The South African Embassy in London denied government
responsibility for the attack.
   ``The ANC is on record as having advocated a policy of violence
... it's very possible this policy has extended to members of the
organization itself,'' said Minister Justus de Goede, the No. 2
diplomat at the embassy.
   The ANC is fighting to topple the South African government and
its policy of apartheid, under which the nation's 26 million blacks
have no voice in national affairs and the 5 million whites control
the economy and dominate government.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
